column13: THE REPORTED PAYMENT REFLECTS THE AMOUNT PROVIDED TO A THIRD PARTY EMPLOYER OR INSTITUTION IN CONNECTION WITH SERVICES PROVIDED BY THE COVERED RECIPIENT.  LILLY DOES NOT KNOW HOW MUCH, IF ANY, OF THIS AMOUNT WAS ACTUALLY RECEIVED BY THE COVERED RECIPIENT.
